From b19b30d8369e74c6c71b72692aa2ac5d4b576394 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harish Rachakonda <rachakon@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 20 Aug 2025 20:48:49 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:CP ath12k: ATF: Add actual airtime relative to radio

Add support to log the percentage of airtime used by a peer relative
to total radio airtime. Reset group total UL airtime and group airtime
counters after printing stats to ensure accurate tracking for
subsequent intervals. This is an additional enhancement based on a request
from CST, while the existing airtime stats implementation is already on par
with proprietary implementation.

